=80=99s sequel to the =E2=80=9CAmerican carnage=E2=80=9D goat rodeo of 2017=
=2E Look no further than the fact that=20=
45/47 delivered, in effect, <em>two </=
em>separate inaugural addresses: the scripted (and decidedly low-energy) of=
ficial rendition in the Capitol Rotunda, followed by the grievance-laden, b=
ackward-looking screed he uncorked a few minutes later to supporters in the=
 Capitol Visitor Center. The second, free-form version felt more familiar
